casebody.data:
Gonzalo HOLGUIN-HERNANDEZ, Petitioner
v.
UNITED STATES No. 18-7739 Supreme Court of the United States. October 21, 2019

Motion of Solicitor General for divided argument granted, and the time is divided *448as follows: 15 minutes for petitioner, 15 minutes for the Solicitor General in support of vacatur, and 30 minutes for Court-appointed amicus curiae in support of the judgment below.
